{"tid":724863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會展板講六七暴動　只提港英警察「暴力鎮壓群眾」　隻字未提炸彈浪潮","createTime":"2018-07-01T09:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T09:20:38.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1eaeb8aa44e9c0b882249e0644bdedbffb3216c9","tid":724863,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">工聯會展板講六七暴動　只提港英警察「暴力鎮壓群眾」　隻字未提炸彈浪潮<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bigwan71cms-03_iFng0_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbigwan71cms-03_iFng0_1200x0.png&h=98f282ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n園足球場連續第二年在七一當日，被親中團體「香港各界慶典委員會」率先租用。場內有多個建制團體擺放展板，工聯會展板雖提到「六七暴動」，但就無說明當年暴徒放炸彈造成平民死亡等，只是強調港英鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n「香港各界慶典委員會」今日下午在維園足球場舉辦展覽等活動，現場人流疏落，在工聯會大灣區主題展覽，有一部分講述「六七暴動」事件，但展板上未有提及「暴動」兩字，只是圖文並茂當年照片，指1967年港英警察暴力鎮壓群眾。<br />\n<br />\n展板提到，同年5月12日工聯會成立「港九各界工人反對港英迫害鬥爭委員會」，於同月舉行「反對港英當局迫害鬥爭大會」，無理被捕的工人在會上控訴港英「暴行」。但六七暴動期間，當年暴徒放炸彈造成平民死亡等，展板則隻字未提。<br />\n<br />\n慶委會今年再度租用維園6個足球場，舉辦以「龍獅躍動大灣區」為題的慶回歸活動，並有多架旅遊巴接載市民到場，致民陣未能以維園球場為七一遊行起點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%95%E6%9D%BF%E8%AC%9B%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%83%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E5%8F%AA%E6%8F%90%E6%B8%AF%E8%8B%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE-%E9%9A%BB%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%AA%E6%8F%90%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E6%B5%AA%E6%BD%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%259D%25BF%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%259C%25BE-%25E9%259A%25BB%25E5%25AD%2597%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E6%25BD%25AE%2F&d=ooyHLuA5Vpqq1UGCPGe%2BRhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1195c896\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%259D%25BF%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2585%25AD%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%259C%25BE-%25E9%259A%25BB%25E5%25AD%2597%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E6%25BD%25AE%2F&h=715b7ca2\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%95%E6%9D%BF%E8%AC%9B%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%83%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E5%8F%AA%E6%8F%90%E6%B8%AF%E8%8B%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE-%E9%9A%BB%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%AA%E6%8F%90%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E6%B5%AA%E6%BD%AE/</a>"},{"pid":"24a05f606a1fc55d11a10e0f4ab1402efc45d6c9","tid":724863,"uid":53498,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"六七唔係暴動,係大英鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n日軍都唔係侵華,係解放蝗蟲"},{"pid":"596faba7113a60d342e806772ec404c8a5a2b3ce","tid":724863,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"你都唔會期望佢哋講出事實啦，過多幾代無人知咩叫放菠蘿"},{"pid":"27529b79b78a07cf70f8c8ee5fc097c62376137d","tid":724863,"uid":59494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a05f606a1fc55d11a10e0f4ab1402efc45d6c9","tid":724863,"uid":53498,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"六七唔係暴動,係大英鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n日軍都唔係侵華,係解放蝗蟲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"南京事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"h